Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.55,0:00:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚喝太多了 头好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办啊 越看越觉得他可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 身体变得好热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真险 真险 差点就稀里糊涂的就羽化了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苇牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲是怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 我没有父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管父亲应该还健在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但母亲就是不肯告诉我们父亲的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酱子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐 你还没有羽化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算参加鹡鸰计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经也有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我被他甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的 人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有喜欢的人一起参加的鹡鸰计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我没任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 苇牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想要我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个 这是 怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能递我酱油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想要我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那话 到底是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 请吃点蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我不是说过 我自己吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是买个东西回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何总是你赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最擅长赛跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定要在买东西大赛中获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你那个座位收入我囊中之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 换一个项目不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就等于认输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何比试中都能取胜的才是正妻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 能为这么悠闲的事情拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 说悠闲是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 算了 月海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小松 发生了什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算逃走的鹡鸰又被惩罚部队灭掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 惩罚部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从帝都逃走的鹡鸰和苇牙的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已然传遍帝都
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走 指在我们的帮助下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走的鷸和久能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个逃出帝都的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予不希望战斗的鹡鸰和苇牙以一线希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 之后成功的例子是 零
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这反而给予他们更深的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵循和平主义的人们 结果也被迫参与战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后看到这些鹡鸰就当做敌人不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果皆人出门 希望大家保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今 似乎出现了哪怕是苇牙也毫不留情攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为 恶魔苇牙 和 死神鹡鸰的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔苇牙 我绝对不想遇到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我想起来了  恶魔苇牙 和 死神鹡鸰的邪恶二人组合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连人也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又白忙活一场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小草
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 椎菜 一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 哥哥的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里 最近好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直没能见到你 你最近怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也有很多事情很忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 和往常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再揉揉小结的大胸胸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胸胸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去你那儿玩行不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚晚饭坐在皆人旁边的会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小结我一定不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该怎样向由佳里解释现在的状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 欺骗了这么多女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后宫？一夫多妻制？龌龊的男女关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人渣透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:57.60,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs50}满\N是\N轻\N蔑\N的\N眼\N神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.60,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs50}不\N想\N接\N近\N所\N以\N斜\N着\N面\N对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:57.60,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs50\pos(30,570)}尽管是妹妹 却比哥哥高年级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.53,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs50\fad(500,500)}哥哥的形象 崩坏…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 也不能说出鹡鸰计划的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们在某地方约见 再一起去吃饭怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噢 就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 在车站前 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在跟谁打电话呢 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳里 好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 以前见过 很可爱而有趣的一个人噢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约了傍晚见面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.77,0:07:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也很关心小结呢 问你最近可好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 小结也好想见到由佳里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 月海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来心情不太好呢 内裤全露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵呢 所以在这儿无所事事呗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天喝酒最爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不论白天黑夜都在喝的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天都在喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 很早以前失恋过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失恋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了治愈受伤的心灵 踏上了长期的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉 就嗜酒如命了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然会认真的听你诉说 我真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你现在还没羽化的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是那次失恋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 或许只是再也没遇到更好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 在与皆人相遇之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没想过这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说是对这种事感到厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在可是与苇牙很亲热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我对皆人的心意不能输给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不也挺好吗 喜欢是不需要理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤全露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没理由说我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且从今开始 不要叫我内裤全露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是没有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上和妹妹约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就不用为我准备晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 下次也叫她来玩噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着护卫的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小松说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就不能让皆人你单独外出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 之后我要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去见妹妹之类的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为正妻 顺便去打个招呼也是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这样的话会发生很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连小结都见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果她连没我这个正妻都没见过话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道对我不是很不公平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.73,0:10:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是这样滴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 No.09在保护着他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我这边还有灰翅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 我想看的电视节目 今天最终回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西让某某人帮你录像下来就行了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诱拐真麻烦 直接打到简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我那种耻辱 仅仅打到怎么能解我心头之气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不让他尝尝精神上的痛苦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视  烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今 帝都的东边有冰峨主宰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西边是真田 南边是御子上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由这三大势力主宰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管目前三大势力的很河蟹的保持均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这种平衡究竟能保持到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花酱 有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒喝完了噢 你有多余的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房的储藏柜里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美哉跟我说不行噢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（乙醇）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.18,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验用酒精 是纯的酒精呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂月海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是下次再介绍你和由佳里见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妻子介绍给家里人 你犹豫个什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 因为鹡鸰计划可是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛 说这便是我心爱的妻子不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也 果然有很多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚部队的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.104 灰翅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚部队也参加了鹡鸰计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来挑起战斗的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然来保护皆人是没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海 我在此接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.09 月海 参上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 呆在这里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是惩罚部队的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.105 红翼噢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好记住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明挑起对决 却又四处逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有何诡计
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正的一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于打算一决胜负了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水祝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水龙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前 不是这么快速的移动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 只是因为皆人被当做人质
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能轻举妄动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也一样噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度应该没事吧 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思 你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度 还有 与那时相同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪儿 这是怎么回事 那个是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是借来用用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能帮我接下电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫大胸女来接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点换No.88来接电话 她肯定在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,88
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我土豆和胡萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在数什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小草 是谁打的电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁都无所谓啦 到底在不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小草可是在这儿噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说你 我是问No.88在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会真喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这可是有伤身体的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,88
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小草 谁来的电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说了我是谁都无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴叫其他的人来接 知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么做究竟是何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你眼前 打倒No.88而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打到小结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 那个奇怪的家伙又会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子输掉 我怎么能咽得下这口气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松酱 换人接电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小草 把这个放下来的话 电话就切断了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切断了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一会 马上就会又打过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又打过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小草的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你不是No.88呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,88？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我就不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁都无所谓 不要敷衍我 快换人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又给我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 到底搞什么 这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让你帮忙会更快捷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是恶作剧电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对方说了No.88呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真纠缠不休呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松我来接
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是皆人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要听这家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了吧 你们的苇牙在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 目标是小结是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 快点叫那家伙来接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不照做 苇牙的生命就没了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然搞什么鬼啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉了 这下子不就不知道电话号码了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 知道自己的立场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会为了自己 而让他人陷入危险中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音恐怕就是No.105红翼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红翼 的确是惩罚部队的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的话 能得出想法就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她试图复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上去找寻皆人的所在位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人的手机 没有反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找到哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会找出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过 逃走事件以来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统安全加强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样快速 潜入MBI的监视卫星的时间也仅有20分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐桥先生被抓走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 松正在搜寻位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你打算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去寻找下下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说的那么狂妄 但其实很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真让我火大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 灰翅也太慢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这家伙那家伙 都让我好烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话中能听到的声音大概就是那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想办法逃走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要逃哪儿去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦 你还真是吵得可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现 又在乱来什么啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:20:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就是被成为梦幻花金杯的名酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这里究竟是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个仓库有好多著名的名酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的找了个很好的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和我干架嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 没有理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的超郁闷 赶快让我解决你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰翅 真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我去拜托碟店老板帮我录像了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是发生了什么事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该只是迟到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会像我们一样与鹡鸰计划有所关联
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 皆人 你到底在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的咖喱 皆人一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花小姐 快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先让那家伙身首异处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越有趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.60,0:23:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前系列中 尽管时常卖弄风情出场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但结束时都没有真正的华丽出场的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹡鸰中第一的美人 强大 魅力满满的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风花我 终于 终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 风花 奋勇的战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.32,0:23:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 你搞错角色了噢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三羽 风的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回也请多多关照咯

