Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.64,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}新しい約束が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:12.64,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}新的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:16.05,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}ココロを強く繋ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:16.05,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}将心紧紧系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.93,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}変わる世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.93,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}瞬息万变的世上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:23.21,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}鐘が響くゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:23.21,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}钟声回响耳边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:26.44,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}終わりなきタタカイが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:26.44,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}没有终结的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:30.07,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}すべてを引き裂いても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:30.07,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}即使一切都已碎裂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:36.18,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}君の微笑みただ信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:36.18,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我依旧只相信你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:40.40,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}あの日の　君の夢守れるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:40.40,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}如果那天 能守护你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.92,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}涙も　痛みさえ抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.92,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}泪水与痛楚我都能拥抱和承受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:47.25,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}刻もう　重ねあうこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:47.25,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}彼此心中刻下的重叠的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:53.19,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}胸の誓い譲れない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:53.19,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我永不会忘记 我心中的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:03:00.18,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}ああ　空の遥か果てまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:03:00.18,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}啊 直到天空那遥远的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:05.11,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}そう　翔てゆくような
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:05.11,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}像这样飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.49,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}加速してく情熱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.49,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}加速燃烧的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:14.27,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}ああ　どんな運命だって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:14.27,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管前方等待的是怎样命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.67,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}そう　高く越えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.67,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我们定能跨越
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:25.77,OPED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(50,50)}負けない勇気くれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:25.77,OPED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}因为你给我了胜利的勇气

